        <div class="two-third individual-content">
            <h2>Meet Dontay</h2>
            <h4>Born October 2003</h4>
            <p>Dontay’s goal is to grow up and study molecules and matter by becoming a chemist. In the meantime, he is happy being a typical pre-teen boy who loves to play video games and sports.</p>
<p>Dontay really likes superheros and enjoys playing the <i>Marvel Heroes</i> video game. He loves watching movies and his favorites are <i>Avatar</i>, <i>Rise of the Guardians</i> and any cartoons. His favorite sport is basketball. Dontay also enjoys watching football, wrestling and baseball on TV. One thing that Dontay says others are surprised to learn about him is that he is really good at playing kickball.<a href="https://www.hckids.org/wp-content/uploads/Dontay-McDade-10-2014.jpg"><img class="  wp-image-2550 alignright" src="https://www.hckids.org/wp-content/uploads/Dontay-McDade-10-2014.jpg" alt="Dontay McDade 10-2014" width="390" height="390" /></a></p>
<p>When it comes to school, Dontay can do really well when he applies himself. He needs a family that can advocate for him academically and encourage him. Dontay’s favorite subjects in school are math and gym class.</p>
<p>Dontay admits that he can be pretty messy. However, as soon as he is asked, Dontay cleans his room and puts all of his clothes and toys away. His meal of choice is Ramen noodles with a dessert of oatmeal cream pie.</p>
<p>What does Dontay want in a forever home? He says that he would like a small family with pets. Dontay feeds the dogs in his current foster home and says he would help take care of an animal. He needs a family to help with cope with separation and loss and better express his emotions.</p>

        </div>
        
